ygData.subject: Re: ppl at Runnyeye
ygData.msgSnippet: curious to know how crowded is Runnyeye for a lvl 18-20+ ? any info on runnyeye is much appreciated. HighHold is getting too crowded with steal killin. HH Pass
ygData.messageBody:
curious to know how crowded is Runnyeye for a lvl 18-20+ ?
any info on runnyeye is much appreciated.

HighHold is getting too crowded with steal killin. HH Pass gives out good
loots and constant stream of orc for good hunt and its so near a zone that u
can run to when in trouble.

Yiyanging at Befallen
